<span id="Description"></span>
== 概要 ==

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
The [[Image:Sketcher_CreatePeriodicBSplineByInterpolation.svg|24px]] [[Sketcher_CreatePeriodicBSplineByInterpolation|Sketcher CreatePeriodicBSplineByInterpolation]] tool creates a periodic (closed) [[B-Splines|B-spline]] curve from knot points. {{Version|1.0}}: This is the same tool as [[Sketcher_CreateBSpline|Sketcher CreateBSpline]] but with a different initial mode.
</div>

<span id="Usage"></span>
== 使い方 ==

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
See also: [[Sketcher_Workbench#Drawing_aids|Drawing aids]].
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:Sketcher_CreatePeriodicBSplineByInterpolation.svg|16px]] [[Sketcher_CreatePeriodicBSplineByInterpolation|Periodic B-Spline From Knots]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|Sketch → Geometries → [[Image:Sketcher_CreatePeriodicBSplineByInterpolation.svg|16px]] Periodic B-Spline From Knots}} option from the menu.
#* Use the keyboard shortcut: {{KEY|G}} then {{KEY|B}}, then {{KEY|O}}.
# For further steps see [[Sketcher_CreateBSpline#Usage|Sketcher CreateBSpline]].
</div>

